# Stage: verify

## Goal

Produce a verify report covering build/lint/unit/integration/e2e/security.

## Inputs

{{#each upstreamArtifacts}}
- `{{this.kind}}` @ `{{this.key}}`
{{/each}}

## Output format

Structured JSON ONLY (no markdown fence):

```json
{
  "build": { "ok": true | false, "command": "<cmd>", "stderr": "..." },
  "lint":  { "ok": true | false, "command": "<cmd>", "issues": [] },
  "unit":  { "ok": true | false, "passed": N, "failed": [{ "name": "...", "repro": "<cmd>" }] },
  "integration": { ... },
  "e2e": { ... },
  "security": { "ok": true | false, "findings": [] }
}
```

## MANDATORY

Every failed assertion includes a `repro` field with a runnable command
that a human (or downstream agent) can paste to reproduce. No exception.

